title: Best of the Program | Guests: Mark Brnovich & Dr. Robert Malone | 3/10/22
description:
Arizona Attorney General Mark Brnovich joins to discuss his Wall Street Journal article “ESG May Be an Antitrust Violation.” Dr. Robert Malone joins to discuss Russia breaking into Ukraine's labs and the possible use of biochemical weapons.
